description:
ANN highlights that Adventist ministry wins 11 Telly Awards in the United States. 

This week, ADRA Canada donated over $700,000 to help refugees in need in Romania. "One Year in Mission and Service" celebrates its fifth anniversary. Adventist youth in Vietnam launch community service to assist people in need. 

Watch as ANN highlights these stories and reports on other news from around the world. 

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our YouTube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news.
